522 template< typename Type // Data type of the matrix
523  , bool SO > // Storage order
524 inline DynamicMatrix<Type,SO>::DynamicMatrix( size_t m, size_t n )
525  : m_ ( m ) // The current number of rows of the matrix
526  , n_ ( n ) // The current number of columns of the matrix
527  , nn_ ( adjustColumns( n ) ) // The alignment adjusted number of columns
528  , capacity_( m_*nn_ ) // The maximum capacity of the matrix
529  , v_ ( allocate<Type>( capacity_ ) ) // The matrix elements
530 {
531  if( IsVectorizable<Type>::value ) {
532  for( size_t i=0UL; i<m_; ++i ) {
533  for( size_t j=n_; j<nn_; ++j ) {
534  v_[i*nn_+j] = Type();
535  }
536  }
537  }
538 
539  BLAZE_INTERNAL_ASSERT( isIntact(), "Invariant violation detected" );
540 }

1303 template< typename Type // Data type of the matrix
1304  , bool SO > // Storage order
1305 template< typename MT // Type of the right-hand side matrix
1306  , bool SO2 > // Storage order of the right-hand side matrix
1307 inline DynamicMatrix<Type,SO>& DynamicMatrix<Type,SO>::operator=( const Matrix<MT,SO2>& rhs )
1308 {
1309  typedef TransExprTrait_<This> TT;
1310  typedef CTransExprTrait_<This> CT;
1311  typedef InvExprTrait_<This> IT;
1312 
1313  if( IsSame<MT,TT>::value && (~rhs).isAliased( this ) ) {
1314  transpose();
1315  }
1316  else if( IsSame<MT,CT>::value && (~rhs).isAliased( this ) ) {
1317  ctranspose();
1318  }
1319  else if( !IsSame<MT,IT>::value && (~rhs).canAlias( this ) ) {
1320  DynamicMatrix tmp( ~rhs );
1321  swap( tmp );
1322  }
1323  else {
1324  resize( (~rhs).rows(), (~rhs).columns(), false );
1325  if( IsSparseMatrix<MT>::value )
1326  reset();
1327  smpAssign( *this, ~rhs );
1328  }
1329 
1330  BLAZE_INTERNAL_ASSERT( isIntact(), "Invariant violation detected" );
1331 
1332  return *this;
1333 }

1714 template< typename Type // Data type of the matrix
1715  , bool SO > // Storage order
1716 void DynamicMatrix<Type,SO>::resize( size_t m, size_t n, bool preserve )
1717 {
1718  using blaze::min;
1719 
1720  if( m == m_ && n == n_ ) return;
1721 
1722  const size_t nn( adjustColumns( n ) );
1723 
1724  if( preserve )
1725  {
1726  Type* BLAZE_RESTRICT v = allocate<Type>( m*nn );
1727  const size_t min_m( min( m, m_ ) );
1728  const size_t min_n( min( n, n_ ) );
1729 
1730  for( size_t i=0UL; i<min_m; ++i ) {
1731  transfer( v_+i*nn_, v_+i*nn_+min_n, v+i*nn );
1732  }
1733 
1734  std::swap( v_, v );
1735  deallocate( v );
1736  capacity_ = m*nn;
1737  }
1738  else if( m*nn > capacity_ ) {
1739  Type* BLAZE_RESTRICT v = allocate<Type>( m*nn );
1740  std::swap( v_, v );
1741  deallocate( v );
1742  capacity_ = m*nn;
1743  }
1744 
1745  if( IsVectorizable<Type>::value ) {
1746  for( size_t i=0UL; i<m; ++i )
1747  for( size_t j=n; j<nn; ++j )
1748  v_[i*nn+j] = Type();
1749  }
1750 
1751  m_ = m;
1752  n_ = n;
1753  nn_ = nn;
1754 }

1790 template< typename Type // Data type of the matrix
1791  , bool SO > // Storage order
1792 inline void DynamicMatrix<Type,SO>::reserve( size_t elements )
1793 {
1794  if( elements > capacity_ )
1795  {
1796  // Allocating a new array
1797  Type* BLAZE_RESTRICT tmp = allocate<Type>( elements );
1798 
1799  // Initializing the new array
1800  transfer( v_, v_+capacity_, tmp );
1801 
1802  if( IsVectorizable<Type>::value ) {
1803  for( size_t i=capacity_; i<elements; ++i )
1804  tmp[i] = Type();
1805  }
1806 
1807  // Replacing the old array
1808  std::swap( tmp, v_ );
1809  deallocate( tmp );
1810  capacity_ = elements;
1811  }
1812 }

1821 template< typename Type // Data type of the matrix
1822  , bool SO > // Storage order
1823 inline DynamicMatrix<Type,SO>& DynamicMatrix<Type,SO>::transpose()
1824 {
1825  using std::swap;
1826 
1827  constexpr size_t block( BLOCK_SIZE );
1828 
1829  if( m_ == n_ )
1830  {
1831  for( size_t ii=0UL; ii<m_; ii+=block ) {
1832  const size_t iend( min( ii+block, m_ ) );
1833  for( size_t jj=0UL; jj<=ii; jj+=block ) {
1834  for( size_t i=ii; i<iend; ++i ) {
1835  const size_t jend( min( jj+block, n_, i ) );
1836  for( size_t j=jj; j<jend; ++j ) {
1837  swap( v_[i*nn_+j], v_[j*nn_+i] );
1838  }
1839  }
1840  }
1841  }
1842  }
1843  else
1844  {
1845  DynamicMatrix tmp( trans(*this) );
1846  this->swap( tmp );
1847  }
1848 
1849  return *this;
1850 }

1859 template< typename Type // Data type of the matrix
1860  , bool SO > // Storage order
1861 inline DynamicMatrix<Type,SO>& DynamicMatrix<Type,SO>::ctranspose()
1862 {
1863  constexpr size_t block( BLOCK_SIZE );
1864 
1865  if( m_ == n_ )
1866  {
1867  for( size_t ii=0UL; ii<m_; ii+=block ) {
1868  const size_t iend( min( ii+block, m_ ) );
1869  for( size_t jj=0UL; jj<ii; jj+=block ) {
1870  const size_t jend( min( jj+block, n_ ) );
1871  for( size_t i=ii; i<iend; ++i ) {
1872  for( size_t j=jj; j<jend; ++j ) {
1873  cswap( v_[i*nn_+j], v_[j*nn_+i] );
1874  }
1875  }
1876  }
1877  for( size_t i=ii; i<iend; ++i ) {
1878  for( size_t j=ii; j<i; ++j ) {
1879  cswap( v_[i*nn_+j], v_[j*nn_+i] );
1880  }
1881  conjugate( v_[i*nn_+i] );
1882  }
1883  }
1884  }
1885  else
1886  {
1887  DynamicMatrix tmp( ctrans(*this) );
1888  swap( tmp );
1889  }
1890 
1891  return *this;
1892 }

1969 template< typename Type // Data type of the matrix
1970  , bool SO > // Storage order
1971 inline bool DynamicMatrix<Type,SO>::isIntact() const noexcept
1972 {
1973  if( m_ * n_ > capacity_ )
1974  return false;
1975 
1976  if( IsVectorizable<Type>::value ) {
1977  for( size_t i=0UL; i<m_; ++i ) {
1978  for( size_t j=n_; j<nn_; ++j ) {
1979  if( v_[i*nn_+j] != Type() )
1980  return false;
1981  }
1982  }
1983  }
1984 
1985  return true;
1986 }

2784 inline EnableIf_<typename DynamicMatrix<Type,SO>::BLAZE_TEMPLATE VectorizedSubAssign<MT> >
2785  DynamicMatrix<Type,SO>::subAssign( const DenseMatrix<MT,SO>& rhs )
2786 {
2787  BLAZE_CONSTRAINT_MUST_BE_VECTORIZABLE_TYPE( Type );
2788  BLAZE_CONSTRAINT_MUST_NOT_BE_DIAGONAL_MATRIX_TYPE( MT );
2789 
2790  BLAZE_INTERNAL_ASSERT( m_ == (~rhs).rows() , "Invalid number of rows" );
2791  BLAZE_INTERNAL_ASSERT( n_ == (~rhs).columns(), "Invalid number of columns" );
2792 
2793  constexpr bool remainder( !usePadding || !IsPadded<MT>::value );
2794 
2795  for( size_t i=0UL; i<m_; ++i )
2796  {
2797  const size_t jbegin( ( IsUpper<MT>::value )
2798  ?( ( IsStrictlyUpper<MT>::value ? i+1UL : i ) & size_t(-SIMDSIZE) )
2799  :( 0UL ) );
2800  const size_t jend ( ( IsLower<MT>::value )
2801  ?( IsStrictlyLower<MT>::value ? i : i+1UL )
2802  :( n_ ) );
2803  BLAZE_INTERNAL_ASSERT( jbegin <= jend, "Invalid loop indices detected" );
2804 
2805  const size_t jpos( ( remainder )?( jend & size_t(-SIMDSIZE) ):( jend ) );
2806  BLAZE_INTERNAL_ASSERT( !remainder || ( jend - ( jend % (SIMDSIZE) ) ) == jpos, "Invalid end calculation" );
2807 
2808  size_t j( jbegin );
2809  Iterator left( begin(i) + jbegin );
2810  ConstIterator_<MT> right( (~rhs).begin(i) + jbegin );
2811 
2812  for( ; (j+SIMDSIZE*3UL) < jpos; j+=SIMDSIZE*4UL ) {
2813  left.store( left.load() - right.load() ); left += SIMDSIZE; right += SIMDSIZE;
2814  left.store( left.load() - right.load() ); left += SIMDSIZE; right += SIMDSIZE;
2815  left.store( left.load() - right.load() ); left += SIMDSIZE; right += SIMDSIZE;
2816  left.store( left.load() - right.load() ); left += SIMDSIZE; right += SIMDSIZE;
2817  }
2818  for( ; j<jpos; j+=SIMDSIZE ) {
2819  left.store( left.load() - right.load() ); left += SIMDSIZE; right += SIMDSIZE;
2820  }
2821  for( ; remainder && j<jend; ++j ) {
2822  *left -= *right; ++left; ++right;
2823  }
2824  }
2825 }

2840 template< typename Type // Data type of the matrix
2841  , bool SO > // Storage order
2842 template< typename MT > // Type of the right-hand side dense matrix
2843 inline void DynamicMatrix<Type,SO>::subAssign( const DenseMatrix<MT,!SO>& rhs )
2844 {
2845  BLAZE_CONSTRAINT_MUST_NOT_BE_SYMMETRIC_MATRIX_TYPE( MT );
2846 
2847  BLAZE_INTERNAL_ASSERT( m_ == (~rhs).rows() , "Invalid number of rows" );
2848  BLAZE_INTERNAL_ASSERT( n_ == (~rhs).columns(), "Invalid number of columns" );
2849 
2850  constexpr size_t block( BLOCK_SIZE );
2851 
2852  for( size_t ii=0UL; ii<m_; ii+=block ) {
2853  const size_t iend( min( m_, ii+block ) );
2854  for( size_t jj=0UL; jj<n_; jj+=block )
2855  {
2856  if( IsLower<MT>::value && ii < jj ) break;
2857  if( IsUpper<MT>::value && ii > jj ) continue;
2858 
2859  for( size_t i=ii; i<iend; ++i )
2860  {
2861  const size_t jbegin( ( IsUpper<MT>::value )
2862  ?( max( ( IsStrictlyUpper<MT>::value ? i+1UL : i ), jj ) )
2863  :( jj ) );
2864  const size_t jend ( ( IsLower<MT>::value )
2865  ?( min( ( IsStrictlyLower<MT>::value ? i : i+1UL ), n_, jj+block ) )
2866  :( min( n_, jj+block ) ) );
2867  BLAZE_INTERNAL_ASSERT( jbegin <= jend, "Invalid loop indices detected" );
2868 
2869  for( size_t j=jbegin; j<jend; ++j ) {
2870  v_[i*nn_+j] -= (~rhs)(i,j);
2871  }
2872  }
2873  }
2874  }
2875 }

4624 template< typename Type > // Data type of the matrix
4625 inline DynamicMatrix<Type,true>& DynamicMatrix<Type,true>::ctranspose()
4626 {
4627  constexpr size_t block( BLOCK_SIZE );
4628 
4629  if( m_ == n_ )
4630  {
4631  for( size_t jj=0UL; jj<n_; jj+=block ) {
4632  const size_t jend( min( jj+block, n_ ) );
4633  for( size_t ii=0UL; ii<jj; ii+=block ) {
4634  const size_t iend( min( ii+block, m_ ) );
4635  for( size_t j=jj; j<jend; ++j ) {
4636  for( size_t i=ii; i<iend; ++i ) {
4637  cswap( v_[i+j*mm_], v_[j+i*mm_] );
4638  }
4639  }
4640  }
4641  for( size_t j=jj; j<jend; ++j ) {
4642  for( size_t i=jj; i<j; ++i ) {
4643  cswap( v_[i+j*mm_], v_[j+i*mm_] );
4644  }
4645  conjugate( v_[j+j*mm_] );
4646  }
4647  }
4648  }
4649  else
4650  {
4651  DynamicMatrix tmp( ctrans(*this) );
4652  this->swap( tmp );
4653  }
4654 
4655  return *this;
4656 }

5514 template< typename Type > // Data type of the matrix
5515 template< typename MT > // Type of the right-hand side dense matrix
5516 inline DisableIf_<typename DynamicMatrix<Type,true>::BLAZE_TEMPLATE VectorizedSubAssign<MT> >
5517  DynamicMatrix<Type,true>::subAssign( const DenseMatrix<MT,true>& rhs )
5518 {
5519  BLAZE_INTERNAL_ASSERT( m_ == (~rhs).rows() , "Invalid number of rows" );
5520  BLAZE_INTERNAL_ASSERT( n_ == (~rhs).columns(), "Invalid number of columns" );
5521 
5522  for( size_t j=0UL; j<n_; ++j )
5523  {
5524  if( IsDiagonal<MT>::value )
5525  {
5526  v_[j+j*mm_] -= (~rhs)(j,j);
5527  }
5528  else
5529  {
5530  const size_t ibegin( ( IsLower<MT>::value )
5531  ?( IsStrictlyLower<MT>::value ? j+1UL : j )
5532  :( 0UL ) );
5533  const size_t iend ( ( IsUpper<MT>::value )
5534  ?( IsStrictlyUpper<MT>::value ? j : j+1UL )
5535  :( m_ ) );
5536  BLAZE_INTERNAL_ASSERT( ibegin <= iend, "Invalid loop indices detected" );
5537 
5538  size_t i( ibegin );
5539 
5540  for( ; (i+2UL) <= iend; i+=2UL ) {
5541  v_[i +j*mm_] -= (~rhs)(i ,j);
5542  v_[i+1+j*mm_] -= (~rhs)(i+1,j);
5543  }
5544  if( i < iend ) {
5545  v_[i+j*mm_] -= (~rhs)(i,j);
5546  }
5547  }
5548  }
5549 }

5566 template< typename Type > // Data type of the matrix
5567 template< typename MT > // Type of the right-hand side dense matrix
5568 inline EnableIf_<typename DynamicMatrix<Type,true>::BLAZE_TEMPLATE VectorizedSubAssign<MT> >
5569  DynamicMatrix<Type,true>::subAssign( const DenseMatrix<MT,true>& rhs )
5570 {
5571  BLAZE_CONSTRAINT_MUST_BE_VECTORIZABLE_TYPE( Type );
5572  BLAZE_CONSTRAINT_MUST_NOT_BE_DIAGONAL_MATRIX_TYPE( MT );
5573 
5574  BLAZE_INTERNAL_ASSERT( m_ == (~rhs).rows() , "Invalid number of rows" );
5575  BLAZE_INTERNAL_ASSERT( n_ == (~rhs).columns(), "Invalid number of columns" );
5576 
5577  constexpr bool remainder( !usePadding || !IsPadded<MT>::value );
5578 
5579  for( size_t j=0UL; j<n_; ++j )
5580  {
5581  const size_t ibegin( ( IsLower<MT>::value )
5582  ?( ( IsStrictlyLower<MT>::value ? j+1UL : j ) & size_t(-SIMDSIZE) )
5583  :( 0UL ) );
5584  const size_t iend ( ( IsUpper<MT>::value )
5585  ?( IsStrictlyUpper<MT>::value ? j : j+1UL )
5586  :( m_ ) );
5587  BLAZE_INTERNAL_ASSERT( ibegin <= iend, "Invalid loop indices detected" );
5588 
5589  const size_t ipos( ( remainder )?( iend & size_t(-SIMDSIZE) ):( iend ) );
5590  BLAZE_INTERNAL_ASSERT( !remainder || ( iend - ( iend % (SIMDSIZE) ) ) == ipos, "Invalid end calculation" );
5591 
5592  size_t i( ibegin );
5593  Iterator left( begin(j) + ibegin );
5594  ConstIterator_<MT> right( (~rhs).begin(j) + ibegin );
5595 
5596  for( ; (i+SIMDSIZE*3UL) < ipos; i+=SIMDSIZE*4UL ) {
5597  left.store( left.load() - right.load() ); left += SIMDSIZE; right += SIMDSIZE;
5598  left.store( left.load() - right.load() ); left += SIMDSIZE; right += SIMDSIZE;
5599  left.store( left.load() - right.load() ); left += SIMDSIZE; right += SIMDSIZE;
5600  left.store( left.load() - right.load() ); left += SIMDSIZE; right += SIMDSIZE;
5601  }
5602  for( ; i<ipos; i+=SIMDSIZE ) {
5603  left.store( left.load() - right.load() ); left += SIMDSIZE; right += SIMDSIZE;
5604  }
5605  for( ; remainder && i<iend; ++i ) {
5606  *left -= *right; ++left; ++right;
5607  }
5608  }
5609 }

5626 template< typename Type > // Data type of the matrix
5627 template< typename MT > // Type of the right-hand side dense matrix
5628 inline void DynamicMatrix<Type,true>::subAssign( const DenseMatrix<MT,false>& rhs )
5629 {
5630  BLAZE_CONSTRAINT_MUST_NOT_BE_SYMMETRIC_MATRIX_TYPE( MT );
5631 
5632  BLAZE_INTERNAL_ASSERT( m_ == (~rhs).rows() , "Invalid number of rows" );
5633  BLAZE_INTERNAL_ASSERT( n_ == (~rhs).columns(), "Invalid number of columns" );
5634 
5635  constexpr size_t block( BLOCK_SIZE );
5636 
5637  for( size_t jj=0UL; jj<n_; jj+=block ) {
5638  const size_t jend( min( n_, jj+block ) );
5639  for( size_t ii=0UL; ii<m_; ii+=block )
5640  {
5641  if( IsLower<MT>::value && ii < jj ) continue;
5642  if( IsUpper<MT>::value && ii > jj ) break;
5643 
5644  for( size_t j=jj; j<jend; ++j )
5645  {
5646  const size_t ibegin( ( IsLower<MT>::value )
5647  ?( max( ( IsStrictlyLower<MT>::value ? j+1UL : j ), ii ) )
5648  :( ii ) );
5649  const size_t iend ( ( IsUpper<MT>::value )
5650  ?( min( ( IsStrictlyUpper<MT>::value ? j : j+1UL ), m_, ii+block ) )
5651  :( min( m_, ii+block ) ) );
5652  BLAZE_INTERNAL_ASSERT( ibegin <= iend, "Invalid loop indices detected" );
5653 
5654  for( size_t i=ibegin; i<iend; ++i ) {
5655  v_[i+j*mm_] -= (~rhs)(i,j);
5656  }
5657  }
5658  }
5659  }
5660 }
